---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';
import Content from '~/components/widgets/Content.astro';
import Stats from '~/components/widgets/Stats.astro';
import WidgetWrapper from '~/components/ui/WidgetWrapper.astro';
import Image from '~/components/common/Image.astro';
import ItemGrid from '~/components/ui/ItemGrid.astro';
import Button from '~/components/ui/Button.astro';
import ItemGrid2 from '~/components/ui/ItemGrid2.astro';
import ZoomableImageGallery from '~/components/ZoomableImageGallery.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'VerifiedX — Tokenized Commerce and Self-Custody for Everyone.',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};

const guiFeatures = [
  {
    image: '~/assets/images/gui/1.jpg',
    title: 'Test 123',
    link: null,
    description: 'lorem ipsum',
  },
];
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero actions={[{ text: 'Learn more', href: '#features', variant: 'primary' }]}>
    <Fragment slot="title">
      Tokenized Commerce and<br />Self-Custody for <span class="text-accent dark:text-primary highlight">Everyone</span
      >.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      <span class="inline font-extralight">
        <span class="font-medium">VerifiedX (<span class="text-primary font-bold">VFX</span>)</span> is an open-source decentralized
        network that is both a <span class="text-primary font-medium">universal layer 1</span> and a <span
          class="text-btc font-medium">Bitcoin sidechain</span
        > for the purpose of tokenized self-custody, on-chain storage, and peer-to-peer commerce of both <span
          class="font-medium">digital</span
        > & <span class="font-medium">physical assets</span>.</span
      >
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Note Widget ******************* -->

  <!-- Features Widget *************** -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-black">
    <h2 class="block font-light text-white text-center text-2xl py-5 bg-gray-900 border-gray-700 border-solid border-t">
      The Verified<span class="text-primary font-bold">X</span> Network
    </h2>
    <Stats
      stats={[
        {
          title: 'Latest Block',
          value: '2,976,494',
          ctaTitle: 'Open Spyglass',
          ctaHref: 'https://spyglass-testnet.verifiedx.io/',
          gradientDirection: 'to bottom right',
        },
        { title: 'Block Time', value: '10', metric: 'seconds', gradientDirection: 'to bottom' },
        { title: 'TXs', value: '1,024', metric: 'per second', gradientDirection: 'to bottom left' },
        { title: 'Fees Burned', value: '1,004.06', metric: 'VFX', gradientDirection: 'to top right' },
        { title: 'Circulating Supply', value: '173,502,020', metric: 'VFX', gradientDirection: 'to top' },
        {
          title: 'Active Validators',
          value: '670',
          ctaHref: '#',
          ctaTitle: 'Start Validating',
          gradientDirection: 'to top left',
        },
      ]}
    />
  </div>

  <section class="background-1 border-t border-gray-800" id="section-discover">
    <WidgetWrapper containerClass={`max-w-6xl mx-auto pt-0 mt-0`}>
      <h2 class={'font-light font-heading text-heading text-5xl text-center tracking-tight '}>
        What Does It All Mean?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base text-center text-primary font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">(And why should we care?)</p>
      <div class="py-5"></div>
      <div class="styled-content-box">
        <div class="font-light text-xl text-white p-5">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-primary">Blockchain can be intimidating for most.</h3>
          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <p>
            It is certainly confusing for the unfamiliar and even the moderately familiar. For starters we need
            technologies that reduce reliance on third parties and help solve everyday problems efficiently with reduced
            costs.
          </p>
          <div class="py-2"></div>
          <p>
            They should provide for seamless everyday interaction by anyone globally and not be reliant on centralized
            authorities to administer them or be based on economic status. Even so, third parties and builders should
            also be empowered to integrate them, with any individual user having a choice to move freely on or off any
            platform and reside completely natively without complication.
          </p>
          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <p>
            Being permissionless, trustless, transparent, and self-sovereign should be as simple and instant as clicking
            a button… this should mean something, this should actually do more than just something. It should empower us
            to manage our own assets freely, securely, and transact with anyone easily, not just rinse and repeat the
            same solutions with a different skin.
          </p>
          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <h3 class="text-3xl text-primary">Welcome to your blockchain, your freedom, your independence...</h3>
          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <p>
            <span class="font-semibold text-primary">VerifiedX</span> is the "peoples network", it is an intuitive on-chain
            utility in everyone's hands. <span class="font-semibold text-primary">VFX</span> takes the mystic and technicalities
            of blockchain and simplifies it for anyone, anytime, and anywhere on any device. It enables simple one-click
            and interactive features and provides simple and immediate on-boarding for any user with a login and password,
            just like any other web app, all while maintaining the highest level of security. Yes, it is plug and play!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </WidgetWrapper>
  </section>

  <section class="border-gray-800 border-t border-b" id="section-vfx">
    <WidgetWrapper containerClass={`max-w-6xl mx-auto`}>
      <div>
        <h2 class={'font-bold font-heading text-heading text-5xl text-center tracking-tight '}>For The People</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base text-center text-primary font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
          <span class="text-white">&ldquo;</span>The people who are crazy enough to think<br />they can change the
          world, are the ones who do.<span class="text-white">&rdquo;</span><br /><span class="text-white"
            >&hyphen; Steve Jobs</span
          >
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xl max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          VerifiedX is the first open-source and completely decentralized universal layer 1 blockchain AND utility
          sidechain for the Bitcoin network. VFX enables tokenized self-custody, data, and peer-to-peer commerce of both
          digital and physical assets. It's built for us, it's built for everyone!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="py-7"></div>

      <ItemGrid
        items={[
          {
            title: 'VFX and BTC',
            description:
              'Send and Receive both VFX and BTC natively. Supports all Bitcoin addresses with a full non-custodial "one-click" user interface!',
            icon: 'tabler:brand-tailwind',
          },
          {
            title: 'Validate for Governance',
            description:
              'Validate by liquid staking in exchange for complete governance. One CPU one vote, with on-chain proposals / voting deployed, actionable, and viewable all through wallets!',
            icon: 'tabler:components',
          },
          {
            title: 'Vault Accounts',
            description:
              ' On-chain Vault accounts, just like a safe deposit box, providing users with the ability to store funds and assets with a "first ever" on-chain recovery and escrow feature eliminating the need for hardware wallets!',
            icon: 'tabler:list-check',
          },
          {
            title: 'Tokenize',
            description:
              'Tokenize any asset, including Bitcoin, and program real on-chain features without any technical knowledge. Mint Non-Fungible (VFX10) and Fungible Tokens (VFX20) with on-chain features by using simple one-click options through self-executing and automated smart contracts for near zero cost, yes gasless!',
            icon: 'tabler:rocket',
          },
          {
            title: 'P2P Commerce',
            description:
              'Trade, lend, borrow, or exhibit directly with anyone anytime through self-custodial published auction houses, shops, bulletins, and galleries with p2p chat and generate direct links to any social media account!',
            icon: 'tabler:arrows-right-left',
          },
          {
            title: 'On-Chain Domains',
            description:
              'Domain name service for all VFX and BTC addresses, simplifying sending and receiving funds and assets that are also transferrable!',
            icon: 'tabler:bulb',
          },
          {
            title: 'Media Beacons',
            description:
              'Complete p2p media and document transfer with privacy and beacon hosting, without the need for third party services!',
            icon: 'tabler:bulb',
          },
          {
            title: 'Easy On/Off Ramps',
            description:
              'Easy in-wallet on / off-ramp for VFX and BTC funds with Apple Pay and Google Pay with integrated providers!',
            icon: 'tabler:bulb',
          },
        ]}
        columns={2}
        classes={{
          container: '',
          title: 'md:text-[1.3rem]',
          icon: 'text-white bg-primary rounded-full w-10 h-10 p-2 md:w-12 md:h-12 md:p-3 mr-4 rtl:ml-4 rtl:mr-0',
        }}
      />

      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center items-center align-middle mt-16">
        <Button variant="primary" href={'#'} class="mx-2">Read Docs</Button>
        <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-primary opacity-40"></div>
        <Button variant="secondary" href={'#'} class="mx-2">Open Deck</Button>
      </div>
    </WidgetWrapper>
  </section>

  <section class="background-2" id="section-bitcoin">
    <WidgetWrapper containerClass={`max-w-6xl mx-auto`}>
      <h2 class={'font-bold font-heading text-heading text-5xl text-center tracking-tight '}>
        Why <span class="text-btc">Bitcoin</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base text-center text-white font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
        <span class="text-white">&ldquo;</span>It's better to be a pirate than join the Navy!<span class="text-white"
          >&rdquo;</span
        ><br /><span class="font-light text-white">&hyphen; Steve Jobs</span>
      </p>
      <div class="py-4"></div>
      <div class="styled-content-box">
        <div class="font-light text-xl text-white p-5">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-btc">Perfected digital capital, digital gold, Apolitical property...</h3>
          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <p>
            Or however you wish to classify Bitcoin, most can agree it has garnered initial critical mass and adoption
            by many… but we are just scratching the surface and getting started! While <span class="font-semibold"
              >VerifiedX</span
            > was built with the same exact ethos and principles of the Bitcoin Network, it isn't a copy of it at all. In
            fact, it has adopted a lot of Bitcoin's security and its philosophy, but it has reiterated over it and added
            smart contract functionalities that have real on-chain features.
          </p>
          <div class="py-2"></div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-btc">These automated features actually solve everyday frictions...</h3>
          <div class="py-2"></div>
          <p>
            And open up doors to many additional self-sovereign possibilities today. <span class="font-semibold"
              >VFX</span
            > not only provides a non-custodial vertically integrated gateway for Bitcoin, but it also serves as a fully
            decentralized sidechain as well. This means that native wallets support all native Bitcoin functions, while also
            helping advance it with true on-chain utility.
          </p>
          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <h3 class="text-3xl text-btc">Think of VerifiedX as a public mall...</h3>

          <div class="py-2"></div>

          <p>
            That is owned by its vendors with Bitcoin as the premier department store. Every single shopper in the
            Bitcoin department store continues to use all the same services and products it always does, except now they
            can walk through the mall and access a host of additional services without leaving their own environment.
            This all happens within ones own control while enhancing the self-sovereign experience, helping scale
            Bitcoin with utility, while dramatically reducing user latency and cost.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </WidgetWrapper>
  </section>

  <section class="border-gray-800 border-t border-b" id="section-vbtc">
    <WidgetWrapper containerClass={`max-w-6xl mx-auto`}>
      <div>
        <h2 class={'font-bold font-heading text-heading text-5xl text-center tracking-tight '}>
          Enter Verified Bitcoin
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base text-center text-secondary text-btc font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
          <span class="text-white">&ldquo;</span>Not Your Daddy's Wrapper<span class="text-white">&rdquo;</span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xl max-w-4xl mx-auto">
