            The <span class="font-semibold">Switchblade</span>
            additionally provides on and off-ramps for both VFX and BTC through integrated solutions via Apple Pay and Google
            Pay providing seamless immediate interaction with the network!
          </p>
          <div class="py-4"></div>

          <ZoomableImageGallery
            images={[
              {
                url: '~/assets/images/gui/1.jpg',
                title: "Switchblade's Dashboard",
                description: 'View all your account information in one place.',
              },
              {
                url: '~/assets/images/gui/3.jpg',
